    • Method Detail

      • doAUCcovUstatistics

        public void doAUCcovUstatistics(java.lang.String flagModality)
        Perform variance analysis with
        -- signal-absent scores t0_modAA, t0_modBB, t0_modAB
        -- signal-present scores t1_modAA, t1_modBB, t1_modAB
        -- signal-absent study design t0_modAA, t0_modBB, t0_modAB
        -- signal-present study design t1_modAA, t1_modBB, t1_modAB
        -- experiment size Nreader, Nnormal, Ndisease.

        -- Creates
        -- AUCsReaderAvg, AUCs -- momentsAA, momentsBB, momentsAB are 1D arrays of length [8]
        -- momentsBiasedAA, momentsBiasedBB, momentsBiasedAB are 1D arrays of length [8]
        -- coefficientsAA, coefficientsBB, coefficientsAB are 1D arrays of length [8]
